21#ifndef GCC_TREE_STDARG_H
22#define GCC_TREE_STDARG_H 1
23
24struct stdarg_info
25{
26 bitmap va_list_vars, va_list_escape_vars;
27 basic_block bb;
28 int compute_sizes, va_start_count;
29 bool va_list_escapes;
30 int *offsets;
31 /* These 2 fields are only meaningful if va_start_count == 1. */
32 basic_block va_start_bb;
33 tree va_start_ap;
34};
